<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201211/4d73e560f0724d608b72b09b5692ff83.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>张 婷</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><strong>《反向流行》主播</strong></span></span><span><strong>、记者</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201211/7020d0033c0344029a76ebc7ea7bfdf3.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
